{"tid":1877289,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警濫捕撿反光衣 稱作非法用","createTime":"2020-02-13T02:32:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-13T03:36:46.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a58999e6ac8399625d816ed1c43b6d33493a19ea","tid":1877289,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T02:32:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200213/PDR5MNOFLEXUFCTGHYFSVTV2HU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200213%2FPDR5MNOFLEXUFCTGHYFSVTV2HU%2F&d=2Od897eOL%2Byk6rGVR7zebQjGR3CVFSgRSSfEWrWQqBA%3D&h=c5c35900\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200213%2FPDR5MNOFLEXUFCTGHYFSVTV2HU%2F&h=eae2cade\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200213/PDR5MNOFLEXUFCTGHYFSVTV2HU/</a><br />\n<br />\n警濫捕撿反光衣 稱作非法用<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200213/large/1581524659_3505.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200213%2Flarge%2F1581524659_3505.jpg&h=ff041c50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警方展示撿獲的救護員反光衣等物品。劉柏麟攝<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】警方濫捕未有因肺炎疫情蔓延而有所收斂，前晚葵青區議員及區內居民在葵聯邨集會，反對在葵盛圍設立指定診所後，有人先後在區內堵路及聚集，警方到場以涉嫌非法集結及藏有工具可作非法用途拘捕12名男女，撿獲急救反光衣、通訊機、頭盔及手套等物品。至於證物中那些涉及可作非法用途，葵青警區刑事助理指揮官姚永勤未有正面回答，只謂「告唔告到會先諮詢律政司意見」。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：被困家庭唯一訴求：盡快回港<br />\n<br />\n葵聯邨集會12人被捕<br />\n<br />\n前晚有份出席居民大會的葵青區議員尹兆堅，認為警方以此理由作拘捕十分離譜，「明顯係莫須有嘅罪名」，又說警方明顯是針對某一代人或對警方不友善的人，稍有差池就會控告。他指早前有市民因攜帶鐵尺被拘捕，有合理辯解的理由亦被拘捕，令被捕人士在抗爭運動中噤聲。<br />\n<br />\n被捕10男2女（14至28歲），當中六人為學生。警方稱前晚10時45分接報在葵聯邨對開有一批人集結叫囂，警員到場截獲12人，並撿獲通訊機、手套、防毒面具、印有急救字樣的反光背心及印有政治訴求的旗幟，於是以涉嫌非法集結及藏有工具可作非法用途拘捕他們。<br />\n<br />\n姚永勤指被捕者無人有急救資格，質疑他們假扮急救員，但被問到警方有否撿獲急救藥物等用品時，姚承認沒有。他稱由於事發前半小時，現場400米外有人曾經堵路，警方會將兩案合併調查。<br />\n<br />\n■記者劉柏麟、江子堯"},{"pid":"7b58649a5ce3c4710664e5c921aa7badabaf8eea","tid":1877289,"uid":2267,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T02:40:50.000Z","msg":"就嚟喺身上搜到Condom都係作非法用途<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"724cd61f0f1c92aefa4277be4fcbd4da12ba4858","tid":1877289,"uid":78046,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T02:52:09.000Z","msg":"無人有急救資格，質疑他們假扮急救員<br />\n急救員係唔需要牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"056a876ad94536b9eab6ccb69ef16b0dc61cf6e0","tid":1877289,"uid":207087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T03:00:16.000Z","msg":"天滅黑警"},{"pid":"0bfca9e41542618c25e2bb00f46c1a8b4f9f641e","tid":1877289,"uid":86314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T03:32:53.000Z","msg":"醫護罷工又話人攪事, 醫護出去救人又話非法用途, 班黑警究竟想醫護點"},{"pid":"3b4da61f5d44eb67f9d05e6465b247548e07b657","tid":1877289,"uid":274722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T03:33:45.000Z","msg":"警濫用保護衣"},{"pid":"c46fd68716d973bfdc8de4bd2ce845491ca9e9eb","tid":1877289,"uid":235015,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7b58649a5ce3c4710664e5c921aa7badabaf8eea","tid":1877289,"uid":2267,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T02:40:50.000Z","msg":"就嚟喺身上搜到Condom都係作非法用途<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T03:35:16.000Z","msg":"錯<br />\n係話你辱警"},{"pid":"6d863ba61b819465cd6cfdcf13370da9a701a1ae","tid":1877289,"uid":70988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"724cd61f0f1c92aefa4277be4fcbd4da12ba4858","tid":1877289,"uid":78046,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20